Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1

(5 comments)

I have few concerns around this change:
1) as Glance is following the normal deprecation policy we should not just remove config options but clearly mark them deprecated if needed.
2) we need to document the migration from the current configuration to the new configuration. Preferably somewhere here: https://github.com/openstack/glance/blame/master/doc/source/configuring.rst#L1570-L1602
3) what is the preference order how osprofiler takes these configs in if they exists in both *-paste.ini and glance-*.conf files? Can we get that documented as well, please.
4) others inline
